{"data":{"post":{"id":"64de3ad9-4113-50ca-830e-0aac0db8f9eb","html":"<h4>2019给贝贝的第一封信</h4>\n<p>亲爱的贝贝：</p>\n<p>  见字如面，幺舅舅很想你们啦，我画了“七彩虹”，想将“七彩虹”送给你，希望你的生活富有色彩。</p>\n<p>  祝亲爱的贝贝：天天开心，身体健康，茁壮成长。</p>\n<p>                          爱你的幺舅舅</p>\n<p>                          2019年01月09日</p>\n<p><figure><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/431ee663fe54ebbe70b8901d429574a2/723b6/letter_1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 72.74484536082474%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"letter 1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/431ee663fe54ebbe70b8901d429574a2/78f2b/letter_1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/431ee663fe54ebbe70b8901d429574a2/dce19/letter_1.jpg 200w,\n/static/431ee663fe54ebbe70b8901d429574a2/c1413/letter_1.jpg 400w,\n/static/431ee663fe54ebbe70b8901d429574a2/78f2b/letter_1.jpg 800w,\n/static/431ee663fe54ebbe70b8901d429574a2/ab4c4/letter_1.jpg 1200w,\n/static/431ee663fe54ebbe70b8901d429574a2/723b6/letter_1.jpg 1552w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a><figcaption class=\"figure-caption\">2019给贝贝的第一副画</figcaption></figure></p>\n<p>亲爱的贝贝：</p>\n<p>  见字如面，你在厦门，还好吗？</p>\n<p>  我这里下雨啦，你听过下雨的声音吗？等厦门下雨的时候，你听听雨声，然后告诉我，你听到了什么，好吗？</p>\n<p>  祝亲爱的贝贝：快乐多多，身体健康，牙齿天天晒太阳。</p>\n<p>                          爱你的幺舅舅</p>\n<p>                          2019年1月10日</p>\n<p><figure><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/795a9727d2d81d794e3d0afab90b7263/52732/letter_s.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 400px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 77.75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"letter s\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/795a9727d2d81d794e3d0afab90b7263/52732/letter_s.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/795a9727d2d81d794e3d0afab90b7263/7f59d/letter_s.jpg 200w,\n/static/795a9727d2d81d794e3d0afab90b7263/52732/letter_s.jpg 400w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a><figcaption class=\"figure-caption\">贝贝第二天画给我的海底世界</figcaption></figure></p>","fields":{"slug":"/2019-01-10/letters-to-beibei/","prefix":"2019-01-10"},"frontmatter":{"title":"2019给贝贝的第一封信","author":"文:Jane","category":"letter","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/431ee663fe54ebbe70b8901d429574a2/ada8c/letter_1.jpg"}}}}},"prev":{"fields":{"slug":"/2019-01-15/accept-your-imperfections/","prefix":"2019-01-15"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Accept your imperfections"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2018-12-22/communicate/","prefix":"2018-12-22"},"frontmatter":{"title":"《沟通的艺术》《非暴力沟通》思维导图"}},"authornote":{"id":"9fe62122-025b-556e-8f79-c5d93f344df9","html":"<p>hustlrb<br>\n<br>\n明德厚学 求是创新</p>"},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"facebook":{"appId":""}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2019-01-10/letters-to-beibei/","total":52,"prev":"/2019-01-15/acce